@startuml
hide footbox
actor 仓管员
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "StockOutOrderController" as Controller
participant "StockOutOrderServiceImpl" as Service
database "MySQL数据库" as DB

仓管员 -> Frontend: 扫描出库单二维码
Frontend -> Controller: GET /stock/outOrder/m/{orderNo}
Controller -> Service: selectStockOutOrderByOrderNo(orderNo)
Service -> DB: 查询出库单及明细
DB --> Service: 返回出库单数据
Service --> Controller: 返回未完成明细
Controller --> Frontend: 返回出库单及明细列表

Frontend -> Frontend: 显示出库明细

group 扫描物料标签
  仓管员 -> Frontend: 扫描标签，匹配明细
  Frontend -> Frontend: 校验货位与数量
  Frontend -> Frontend: 累加扫码数量
end

仓管员 -> Frontend: 确认提交
Frontend -> Controller: POST /stock/outOrder/submitStockOut
Controller -> Service: submitStockOut(username, requestBody)

group 事务处理每个物料
  Service -> DB: 扣减库存数量
  Service -> DB: 更新出库明细已领数量
  Service -> DB: 插入出库流水记录
end

Service -> DB: 更新出库单状态
Service --> Controller: 返回操作结果
Controller --> Frontend: 返回成功响应
Frontend --> 仓管员: 出库完成

@enduml